additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Household Warnings: KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN Pharmaceutical Warnings: Formulated Supplementary Food. You will need to include a description of the role of the food as a supplement to a normal diet to address situations where intakes of energy and nutrients may not be adequate to meet and individual's requirements. Please ensure product is labelled in accordance with the Australia New Zealand Food Std's Code, Formulated Meal Replacement and Formulated Supplementary Foods. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (phone Australia 13 11 26) or a doctor.
